0be%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20load%20off%20of%20you.%20As%20an%20example%2C%20one%20thing%20that%20every%20developer%20has%20to%20do%20is%20make%20commit%20messages.%20You%20write%20some%20code%2C%20you%20do%20your%20work%2C%20and%20you%20save%20it%2C%20basically%2C%20to%20a%20checkpoint.%20You%20write%20a%20message%20about%20what%20you're%20saving.%20It%20seems%20no%20one%20has%20ever%20really%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20into%20that.%20Now%2C%20you%20just%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20write%20me%20a%20good%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20AI%20writes%20incredible%2C%20detailed%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20you'd%20always%20see%20messages%20like%20%26quot%3Bwork%20in%20progress%26quot%3B%20or%20totally%20unusable%20stuff.%20Even%20if%20it%20was%20kind%20of%20useful%2C%20AI%20adds%20a%20lot%20more%20detail.%20Now%2C%20I%20never%20have%20to%20think%20about%20what%20I%20have%20to%20write%20for%20that.%20That's%20only%20one%20tiny%20slice%20of%20the%20whole%20big%20picture%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ebb9d9f6-9846-420c-8bfa-7b711a87a870%5C%22%3EAI%20will%20make%20you%20better%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20AI%2C%20it%20almost%20feels%20like%20you%20have%20another%20person%20with%20you%20at%20all%20times%20that%20you%20can%20ask%20anything%20you%20need%20to%20or%20try%20to%20brainstorm%20with.%20Before%2C%20it%20was%20all%20on%20you.%20It's%20crazy%20to%20me%20to%20think%20about%20going%20a%20day%20without%20using%20it%2C%20even%20though%20it's%20only%20been%20a%20year%20or%20two%20since%20this%20came%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-agents-adoption-top-tools-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewrite%20an%20entire%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20in%20days%2C%20where%20before%20it%20would%20have%20taken%20me%20months.%20For%20example%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20have%20a%20side%20business%20developing%20software%20for%20sales%20agencies