vesting%2Fbest-crypto-bitcoin-exchanges%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecentralized%20crypto%20exchanges%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20performance%20issues%2C%20like%20not%20being%20able%20to%20process%20orders%20quickly.%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20with%20the%20same%20efficiency%20you'd%20expect%20from%20traditional%20finance%2C%20but%20in%20a%20more%20decentralized%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20was%20so%20nascent%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20once-in-a-generation%20opportunity%20where%20someone%20like%20me%2C%20who%20didn't%20have%20industry%20experience%20or%20a%20lot%20of%20academic%20knowledge%2C%20could%20jump%20in%20and%20contribute%20value%20right%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fall%20of%202018%2C%20I%20took%20a%20leave%20of%20absence%20from%20college%20and%20officially%20started%20Injective.%20I%20got%20a%20cofounder%20to%20help%20split%20up%20the%20engineering%20and%20research%20tasks.%20We%20recruited%20engineering%20talent%20so%20we%20could%20build%20out%20our%20own%20exchange%20product%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20figuring%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteps-how-to-launch-small-business-entrepreneur-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20operate%20a%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20get%20investor%20buy-in%2C%20I%20engaged%20with%20other%20people%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20including%20my%20contacts%20from%20the%20fund%20I%20worked%20at%2C%20but%20I%20also%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20lot%20of%20stuff%20by%20myself.%20The%20industry%20was%20so%20new%20that%20people%20who'd%20worked%20in%20it%20for%20a%20while%20didn't%20have%20standardized%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20some%20college%20courses%20on%20the%20side%20because%20my%20parents%20encouraged%20me%20not%20to%20drop%20out%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20in%202020%2C%20I%20decided%20not%20to%20devote%20any%20more%20time%20to%20finishing%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fbaf9e6-