ctivity-tool-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Cuban%3C%2Fa%3E%20speak%20at%20Harvard%2C%20where%20he%20shared%20his%20email%20for%20people%20to%20pitch%20him%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20team%20decided%20to%20pitch%20him.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-learned-from-gamestop-squeeze-and-robinhood-saga-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGameStop%20saga%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20causing%20upheaval%20because%20Robinhood%20had%20prevented%20people%20from%20buying%20GameStop%20stock.%20Mark%20Cuban%20commented%20publicly%20on%20it.%20In%20our%20pitch%2C%20we%20spoke%20to%20that%20moment%20and%20shared%20that%20we%20were%20building%20an%20open%20platform%20with%20no%20entity%20that%20could%20control%20what%20people%20can%20or%20can't%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20kicked%20off%20a%20whole%20email%20chain%20in%20which%20Mark%20asked%20us%20questions%20about%20our%20solution%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20answer%20as%20accurately%20and%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20After%20a%20bit%20of%20back-and-forth%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20invest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20strategy%20was%20to%20be%20down-to-earth%2C%20so%20we%20were%20honest%20about%20our%20product%20and%20not%20upselling%20it%20or%20exaggerating%20what%20we%20could%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20we've%20raised%20over%20%2450%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f20fc850-095d-41dc-964b-a744a494770e%5C%22%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20took%20advantage%20of%20an%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20few%20years%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdropped-out-high-school-college-astill-became-ceo-brez-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleaving%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20the%20most%20challenging%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20constantly%20drowning%20in%20work%20and%20felt%20pressure%20to%20make%20things%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20a%20strong%20dissatisfaction%20with%20col