t%20startup%20at%20our%20size%20%E2%80%94%20that%20has%20not%20been%20done%20before.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20do%2C%20but%20it%20is%20doable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20many%20measures%2C%20the%20reset%20is%20working.%20Amazon's%20stock%20is%20up%20more%20than%2030%25%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20outperforming%20the%20tech-heavy%20Nasdaq.%20Amazon's%20profit%20per%20employee%20rose%20to%20%2444%2C100%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20five%20times%20the%202022%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20think%20creativity%20suffered%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20and%20for%20sure%20the%20cohesive%20culture%20that%20was%20peculiar%20to%20Amazon%20also%20suffered%2C%26quot%3B%20Babak%20Parviz%2C%20a%20former%20Amazon%20vice%20president%20who%20is%20now%20running%20his%20own%20AI%20healthcare%20startup%20NewDays%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAndy%20is%20rightfully%20focusing%20on%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20Amazon%20culture%20is%20maintained%20and%20thriving%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20dissipate%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20under%20Jassy's%20leadership%2C%20Amazon%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20corporate%20America's%20cultural%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-hardcore-era-employee-changes-att-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshift%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20all%20tightened%20their%20performance%20expectations%2C%20though%20their%20return%20to%20the%20office%20mandates%20are%20still%20less%20strict%20than%20Amazon's.%20Old%20guard%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-ceo-john-stankey-email-employee-feedback-survey-rto-policy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAT%26amp%3BT%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20similarly%20taken%20a%20stricter%20stance%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-ceo-memo-workplace-loyalty-dead-employees-job-security-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffice%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Jassy%20enters%20his%20fifth%20year%20leading%20Amazon%2C%20his%20leadership%20has%20been%20defined%20less%20by%20any%20single%20product%20or%20splashy%20hire%2C%20but%20rather%20by%20his%20revamp%20of%20Amazon's%20culture%20as%20he%20tries%20to%20recapture%20Bezos'%20%26quot%3Balways%20Day%201%26quot%3B%20mindset%20and%20position%20the%20tech%20giant%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20close%20reading%20of%20that%20effort%20%E2%80%94%20Jassy's%20hardline%20approach%20to%20employee%20management%20and%20of%20his%20laser%20focus%20on%20a%20more%20nimble%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-hardcore-era-employee-changes-att-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edo-more-with-less%3C%2Fa%3E%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20has%20created%20a%20playbook%20that%20leaders%20of%20companies%20large%20and%20small%20could%20study%2C%20even%20if%20not%20everyone%20would%20embrace%20his%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20return%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-hardcore-era-employee-changes-att-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehardcore%3C%2Fa%3E%20mindset%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20growing%20concern%20among%20Jassy%20and%20his%20top%20brass%20that%20the%20tech%20giant's%20famously%20scrappy%2C%20ruthlessly%20efficient%20culture%20had%20taken%20a%20hit%20during%20the%20company's%20years%20of%20explosive%20growth%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20their%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayers%20of%20bureaucracy%2C%20which%20had%20settled%20like%20sediment%20as%20the%20company%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20were%20slowing%20things%20down%2C%20struggling%20initiatives%20needed%20to%20be%20streamlined%2C%20and%20a%20flexible%20work-from-home%20policy%20meant%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20employees%20who'd%20joined%20during%20and%20after%20the%20pandemic%20had%20never%20been%20properly%20integrated%20into%20Amazon's%20way%20of%20doing%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20zeroed%20in%20on%20the%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20culture%20early%20on%20in%20his%20tenure%20as%20CEO.%20But%20it%20was%20a%20few%20years%20before%20he%20and%20his%20senior%20leadership%20were%20able%20to%20do%20much%20about%20it%2C%20according%20to%20Drew%20Herdener%2C%20the%20company's%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20communications%20and%20corporate%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202021%2C%20when%20Jassy%20replaced%20founder%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20became%20Amazon's%20second-ever%20CEO%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20was%20expanding%20at%20a%20breakneck%20pace.%20A%20hiring%20spree%20of%20historic%20proportions%20had%20minted%20Amazon%20as%20the%20second%20biggest%20private%20employer%20in%20the%20US%2C%20after%20Walmart.%20The%20company%20was%20also%20on%20track%20to%20eclipse%20Walmart%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20retailer%20outside%20China%2C%20with%20a%20delivery%20network%20to%20rival%20UPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20Amazon%20went%20on%20a%20rollercoaster%20of%20devastating%20losses%20and%20extraordinary%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202022%2C%20as%20the%20bottom%20fell%20out%20of%20the%20pandemic%20boom%2C%20Amazon%20became%20the%20first%20company%20to%20shed%20%241%20trillion%20in%20market%20value%20%E2%80%94%20a%20figure%20just%20shy%20of%20the%20entire%20value%20of%20Alphabet%2C%20Google's%20parent%20company.%20Senior%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-executive-exodus-vps-other-senior-people-leaving-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutives%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-executive-exodus-vps-other-senior-people-leaving-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleaving%20in%20droves%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20an%20internal%20report%20at%20the%20time%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20bluntly%20warned%20that%20Amazon's%20public%20image%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20need%20of%20immediate%2C%20significant%20repair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Batnick%2C%20director%20of%20research%20at%20Ritholtz%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20even%20floated%20the%20idea%20on%20CNBC%20that%20Bezos%20might%20need%20to%20return%20as%20CEO%20%26quot%3Bto%20steady%20the%20ship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20by%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20Amazon%20had%20laid%20off%20nearly%2030%2C000%20employees%2C%20streamlined%20its%20cost%20structure%2C%20and%20downsized%20a%20number%20of%20projects%2C%20including%20its%20moonshot%20lab%20Grand%20Challenge.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAmazon%20had%20not%20only%20stemmed%20its%20losses%20but%20surpassed%20a%20%242%20trillion%20market%20cap%2C%20and%20Jassy%20was%20being%20credited%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-andy-jassy-wooed-wall-street-overhauled-bloated-tech-giant-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextraordinary%20turnaround%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20dust%20had%20settled%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sense%20that%20Amazon%20would%20need%20to%20better%20integrate%20the%20surge%20of%20new%20hires%20from%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20pandemic%20into%20Amazon's%20corporate%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20executive%20noted%20that%20maintaining%20Amazon's%20famed%20memo-writing%20culture%20was%20especially%20challenging%20for%20new%20hires%20more%20accustomed%20to%20PowerPoint%20presentations.%20Many%20also%20struggled%20to%20fully%20embrace%20the%20company's%20Leadership%20Principles%2C%20which%20are%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20how%20Amazon%20operates.%20Productivity%20slipped%2C%20and%20as%20Jassy%20puts%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Briffing%26quot%3B%20on%20new%20ideas%20got%20harder%20with%20remote%20work.%20While%20it%20reached%20record%20profits%2C%20Amazon%20grappled%20with%20the%20layers%20of%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20growing%20perception%20of%20falling%20behind%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20more%20difficult%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20new%20employees%20really%20understood%20what%20the%20culture%20was%2C%20just%20because%20it%20was%20growing%20so%20fast.%26quot%3B%20Parviz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20last%20fall%2C%20Jassy%20was%20pressing%20that%20culture%20reset%20and%20his%20war%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-explains-why-he-wants-fewer-managers-hate-bureaucracy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon's%20bureaucracy%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20full%20throttle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EA%20glimpse%20into%20Amazon's%20more%20disciplined%2C%20hardcore%20culture%20came%20in%20July%2C%20when%20an%20Amazon%20advertising%20director%20sent%20senior%20managers%20a%20sharply%20worded%20email%20titled%20%26quot%3BRaising%20Our%20Leadership%20Standard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20wanted%20to%20see%20%26quot%3Bhigher%20productivity%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmore%20competitive%20leadership%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20the%20email%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20need%20every%20leader%20on%20this%20team%20to%20step%20into%20the%20arena%20and%20commit%20to%20this%20higher%20standard.%20If%20they%20can't%20or%20won't%2C%20I%20need%20them%20to%20leave%20ASAP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20email%20is%20%26quot%3Bunrelated%20to%20or%20reflective%20of%20Andy's%20strengthening%20our%20culture%20and%20teams%20initiative.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20Amazon's%20culture%20has%20always%20been%20%26quot%3Bperformance-driven%20and%20fast-paced%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20back%20to%20our%20roots%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20staff%20meetings%2C%20company%20executives%20hammer%20home%20the%20importance%20of%20frugality%2C%20making%20it%20a%20recurring%20theme%20in%20internal%20discussions%20and%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20said%20at%20a%20company%20staff%20meeting%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20record%20of%20which%20was%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20would%20I%20do%20if%20this%20was%20my%20money%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20leaders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-andy-jassy-manager-fiefdoms-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJassy%20stressed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20those%20who%20%26quot%3Bget%20the%20most%20done%20with%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20resources%20required%20to%20do%20the%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20also%20revamped%20its%20compensation%20system%20to%20reward%20high%20performers%20more%20directly.%20The%20new%20structure%20puts%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20an%20employee's%20performance%20history%2C%20with%20those%20earning%20top%20marks%20for%20four%20consecutive%20years%20now%20eligible%20for%20pay%20increases%20that%20exceed%20the%20standard%20compensation%20bands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy's%20latest%20push%20has%20been%20to%20reinforce%20Amazon's%20operating%20DNA%2C%20which%20centers%20on%20the%20company's%20Leadership%20Principles%20%E2%80%94%20the%2016%20core%20values%20that%20shape%20decision-making%20at%20every%20level%20and%20are%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20how%20Amazon%20operates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20company%20formally%20incorporated%20adherence%20to%20those%20principles%20into%20performance%20reviews%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20tying%20them%20directly%20to%20pay%20and%20promotions.%20That%20followed%20a%20new%20video%20series%20Jassy%20launched%20last%20year%2C%20breaking%20down%20each%20principle%2C%20from%20%26quot%3BCustomer%20Obsession%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BFrugality%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BDisagree%20and%20Commit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20at%20Amazon%20now%20for%2027%20years%2C%20and%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20I%20still%20consider%20myself%20a%20student%20of%20our%20Leadership%20Principles%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20announcing%20the%20launch%20of%20an%20internal%20video%20series%20explaining%20his%20take%20on%20each%20LP.%20%26quot%3BI%20work%20hard%20at%20it%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20changes%20have%20come%20with%20headaches.%20The%20return-to-office%20rollout%20has%20been%20bumpy%2C%20with%20complaints%20about%20desk%20shortages%20and%20other%20logistical%20headaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComplaints%20have%20also%20come%20from%20middle-managers%2C%20who%20say%20they're%20now%20spending%20far%20more%20time%20overseeing%20ever-larger%20teams%2C%20leading%20to%20longer%20hours%20and%20a%20drop%20in%20personal%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJunior%20leaders%20say%20that%20major%20decisions%20are%20made%20by%20a%20tight-knit%20group%20of%20top%20Amazon%20leaders%20and%20that%20they%20are%20often%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20loop.%20Last%20year%2C%20for%20example%2C%20when%20Jassy%20announced%20a%20full%20five-day%20return-to-office%20mandate%20and%20a%20push%20to%20slim%20down%20middle%20management%2C%20multiple%20VPs%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20learned%20about%20the%20changes%20from%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20unsentimental%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20executive%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20numbers%20don't%20work%2C%20they%20just%20move%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20complain%20that%20cost-cutting%20has%20veered%20into%20micromanagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20AWS%2C%20some%20employees%20now%20report%20what%20percentage%20of%20their%20phone%20use%20is%20work-related%2C%20with%20the%20%2450%20monthly%20reimbursement%20adjusted%20proportionally.%20In%20retail%2C%20employees%20have%20complained%20they%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emust%20now%20seek%20approval%20for%20business%20trips%20by%20outlining%20expected%20goals%20and%20projected%20returns.%20They%20also%20need%20to%20break%20down%20expenses%20by%20meal%20to%20give%20more%20details%20about%20their%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20and%20his%20wife%20Elana%20Jassy%20at%20the%20Sun%20Valley%20Conference%20in%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b1d05da17a8c5b4053beea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222192%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20CEO%2C%20Jassy%20has%20slashed%20layers%20of%20management%20and%20sent%20his%20350%2C000%20corporate%20employees%20back%20to%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Amazon%20employees%20say%20they%20fear%20for%20their%20job%20security%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20after%20Jassy's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-employees-criticize-ceo-jassys-ai-driven-job-cutting-plan-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20prediction%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Befficiency%20gains%26quot%3B%20accomplished%20with%20AI%20would%20lead%20to%20an%20even%20smaller%20white-collar%20workforce.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20really%20hard%20for%20people%20to%20show%20up%20at%20work%20and%20be%20all-in%20knowing%20tomorrow%20might%20be%20the%20last%20day%20at%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20current%20Amazon%20executive%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20already%20being%20jammed%20into%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20business%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20pressure%2C%20employees%20say.%20Some%20teams%20now%20track%20performance%20by%20how%20frequently%20staff%20use%20AI%20tools%2C%20while%20others%20treat%20having%20an%20AI%20project%20as%20little%20more%20than%20a%20box%20to%20tick.%20Several%20employees%20describe%20the%20result%20as%20%26quot%3BAI%20fatigue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Amazonians%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20give%20Jassy%20credit%20for%20being%20personable%20and%20operating%20with%20a%20more%20people-focused%20leadership%20style.%20One%20former%20executive%20recalled%20Jassy%20taking%20time%20during%20meetings%20to%20get%20to%20know%20him%20personally%2C%20a%20gesture%20that%20earned%20his%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20level%20of%20care%20to%20make%20it%20more%20humane%20is%20a%20tremendous%20motivator%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EJassy's%20cost%20discipline%20also%20reflects%20a%20deeper%20shift%20in%20Amazon's%20philosophy.%20Unlike%20Bezos%2C%20who%20spread%20bets%20widely%20across%20hundreds%20of%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20from%20satellite%20internet%20to%20healthcare%20moonshots%20%E2%80%94%20Jassy%20prefers%20to%20concentrate%20on%20a%20few%20dozen%20initiatives%20he%20considers%20big%20bets%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJassy%20wants%20to%20focus%20on%20things%20that%20Amazon%20is%20uniquely%20positioned%20to%20do%20a%20good%20job%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20VP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20CEO%20has%20grown%20skeptical%20of%20an%20internal%20metric%20known%20as%20downstream%20impact%2C%20or%20DSI%2C%20the%20same%20former%20VP%20said.%20This%20measure%20attempts%20to%20estimate%20a%20project's%20lifetime%20value%20using%20imprecise%20indicators%2C%20such%20as%20how%20Alexa%20might%20indirectly%20boost%20the%20number%20of%20shoppers%20on%20Amazon.%20The%20voice%20assistant%2C%20once%20a%20flagship%20product%2C%20was%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-alexa-job-layoffs-rise-and-fall-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20units%20to%20be%20downsized%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20Jassy%20due%20to%20its%20mounting%20losses%20and%20the%20team's%20failure%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20Jassy%20has%20shown%20particular%20support%20for%20high-margin%20businesses%20such%20as%20cloud%20computing%20and%20advertising%2C%20this%20person%20added.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20Amazon%20introduced%20ads%20to%20its%20video%20streaming%20service%20and%20ramped%20up%20investment%20in%20cloud%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bpursuing%20as%20many%20if%20not%20more%20projects%20in%20more%20focused%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20pace%20of%20innovation%20is%20only%20accelerating%20under%20Jassy.%20The%20leadership%20team%20is%20improving%20its%20%26quot%3Banalysis%20of%20DSI%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20stop%20measuring%20it%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20with%20so%20much%20focus%20on%20cost%20cutting%2C%20there's%20mounting%20worry%20among%20Amazon's%20rank%20and%20file%20that%20Amazon%20is%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20appeal%20to%20top%20talent%20and%20position%20itself%20as%20a%20great%20place%20to%20work.%20(Amazon's%20spokesperson%20disputed%20this%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Binterest%20in%20joining%20Amazon%20remains%20as%20strong%20as%20it's%20ever%20been.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20worry%20dates%20back%20to%20late%20last%20year%2C%20just%20as%20Jassy's%20reset%20plan%20was%20coming%20into%20focus.%20An%20internal%20document%20created%20by%20Amazon's%20recruiting%20team%20and%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20noted%20that%20the%20rigid%20RTO%20mandate%20and%20the%20company's%20unique%20pay%20model%20are%20making%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-talent-wars-internal-document-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharder%20to%20recruit%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20demand%26quot%3B%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenAI%20hiring%20faces%20challenges%20like%20location%2C%20compensation%2C%20and%20Amazon's%20perceived%20lag%20in%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%20%26quot%3BCompetitors%20often%20provide%20more%20comprehensive%20and%20aggressive%20packages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Amazon%20recruiter%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20job%20candidates%20last%20year%20had%20cited%20Amazon's%20RTO%20policy%20when%20declining%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20losing%20out%20on%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-amazons-hardcore-culture-reset-day-1-roots-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756800421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a88a17cfc04e97619bdab6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-amazons-hardcore-culture-reset-day-1-roots-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20is%20yanking%20the%20company%20back%20to%20its%20roots%2C%20from%20RTO%20to%20monitoring%20employee%20phone%20use%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ekim%40businessinsider.com%20(Eugene%20Kim)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-amazons-hardcore-culture-reset-day-1-roots-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suicide%20Behind%20One%20In%20Every%20100%20Deaths%3A%20WHO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22More%20than%20one%20in%20every%20100%20deaths%20globally%20is%20due%20to%20suicide%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20said%20Tuesday%2C%20calling%20for%20urgent%20action%20to%20stem%20a%20mounting%20mental%20health%20crisis%20among%20young%20people%20especially.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756800204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F2sl5qfqg_kota-student-suicide-generic_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-health-organization-says-suicide-behind-one-in-every-100-d