ralvagonzavod's%20main%20tank%20factory%20in%20the%20Urals.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b680e0a17a8c5b4053d78a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPutin%20visited%20the%20Uralvagonzavod%20plant%20in%20February%202024.%3Cp%3EALEXANDER%20KAZAKOV%2FPOOL%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229db974a1-2e32-41cf-96c5-1a12d2a57fa8%5C%22%3EUS%20and%20European%20equipment%20making%20T-series%20tanks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20GUR's%20list%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwar-sanctions.gur.gov.ua%2Ftools%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen%20to%20the%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Uralvagonzavod%20has%20been%20recorded%20using%20at%20least%20148%20types%20of%20equipment%20made%20by%20manufacturers%20in%20NATO%20member%20states%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%2042%20types%20of%20equipment%20were%20listed%20as%20coming%20from%20manufacturers%20in%20European%20and%20Asian%20nations%2C%20such%20as%20Austria%2C%20China%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea.%20GUR's%20catalogue%20indicates%20that%20Uralvagonzavod%20operates%20multiple%20units%20of%20some%20equipment%20types%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20total%20of%20260%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExamples%20include%20American-made%20vertical%20lathe%20machines%20that%20lift%2C%20hold%2C%20and%20rotate%20heavy-duty%20equipment%2C%20German%20computer-controlled%20machining%20centers%2C%20and%20Italian%20press%20brakes%20for%20bending%20metal%20into%20precise%20shapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUralvagonzavod%20is%20known%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-demand-tanks-outstrips-production-by-factor-of-10-report-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia's%20sole%20major%20tank%20manufacturer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20its%20flagship%20plant%20in%20the%20Ural%20Mountains%20serving%20as%20the%20Kremlin's%20armored%20vehicle%20hub.%20During%20the%20war%2C%20main%20battle%20tank%20production%20at%20its%20factory%20complex%20has%20reportedly%20hovered%20at%2020%20to%2030%20new%20tanks%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224485%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dmitry%20Medvedev%2C%20flanked%20by%20officials%20and%20followed%20by%20staff%2C%20visits%20Uralvagonzavod's%20tank%20production%20plant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b681fa194a2d49b8af8a40%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222990%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDmitry%20Medvedev%2C%20Russia's%20former%20president%20who%20is%20now%20second%20in%20rank%20to%20Putin%20in%20the%20Kremlin's%20security%20council%2C%20visited%20the%20plant%20in%20November%202024.%3Cp%3EYEKATERINA%20SHTUKINA%2FPOOL%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGUR%20said%20that%20the%20firm%20launched%20a%20new%20production%20plant%20in%202024%20for%20building%20tank%20engines%2C%20and%20that%20the%20site%20is%20%26quot%3Bequipped%20with%20high-tech%20CNC%20machines%20from%20leading%20European%20manufacturers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20deliveries%20to%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20through%20third%20countries%20continue%2C%20although%20they%20have%20become%20more%20complicated%2C%20longer%2C%20and%20more%20expensive%20due%20to%20the%20sanctions%20introduced%2C%26quot%3B%20GUR's%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20GUR%20says%20it's%20collected%20evidence%20of%201%2C396%20foreign-made%20machines%20used%20in%20169%20factories%20across%20Russia%20that%20supply%20Moscow's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20each%20piece%20of%20equipment%2C%20GUR%20publishes%20Russian%20government%20procurement%20documents%2C%20videos%20shot%20in%20factories%2C%20or%20leasing%20agreements%20that%20it%20says%20are%20evidence%20of%20such%20tools%20being%20used%20in%20the%20Kremlin's%20industrial%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C