0unpleasant%26quot%3B%20experience%20when%20he%20first%20joined%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20government%20efficiency%20commission%2C%20DOGE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20back%20to%20February%2C%20when%20I%20got%20involved%2C%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20were%20neutral%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20were%20positive%2C%20and%20then%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20people%20who%20were%20just%20hateful%2C%26quot%3B%20Gebbia%20said%20in%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Katie%20Miller%20Podcast%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aired%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%2C%20who%20is%20married%20to%20Stephen%20Miller%2C%20the%20White%20House's%20deputy%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20was%20previously%20DOGE's%20communications%20lead.%20She%20left%20DOGE%20in%20May%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkatie-miller-doge-elon-musk-advisor-launch-podcast-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estarted%20her%20namesake%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20thinking%2C%20if%20it's%20a%20stranger%20on%20the%20internet%20calling%20you%20something%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20big%20deal.%20But%20if%20it's%20somebody%20that%20you%20worked%20with%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20it%20hits%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Gebbia%20said%20without%20specifying%20who%20his%20detractors%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Gebbia%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Gebbia%20announced%20on%20X%20that%20he%20was%20joining%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20DOGE%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20his%20post%2C%20which%20was%20published%20on%20February%2027%2C%20Gebbia%20said%20his%20first%20project%20would%20be%20to%20improve%20the%20%26quot%3Bslow%20and%20paper-based%20retirement%20process%26quot%3B%20for%20federal%