%20Warp%2C%20an%20AI%20agent%20platform%20for%20developers.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Li%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAdvait%20Maybhate%2C%2024%2C%20is%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Warp%2C%20an%20AI%20agent%20platform%20for%20developers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMaybhate%20did%20a%20dozen%20internships%20before%20graduating%20from%20college%20in%202023.%20Two%20of%20them%20were%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he%20chose%20to%20work%20at%20a%20startup%20instead%20of%20a%20Big%20Tech%20company%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Advait%20Maybhate%2C%20a%20software%20engineer.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20employment%20and%20academic%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20graduated%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Waterloo%20with%20my%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%202023%2C%20I%20had%20done%20about%20a%20dozen%20tech%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternships%20are%20a%20big%20deal%20at%20Waterloo%2C%20and%20students%20usually%20do%20six%20during%20their%20time%20there.%20I%20started%20doing%20internships%20before%20I%20enrolled%20and%20took%20some%20gap%20semesters%20to%20squeeze%20in%20a%20couple%20more%20stints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-wage-internship-arms-race-to-clinch-dream-jobs-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einter%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-wage-internship-arms-race-to-clinch-dream-jobs-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enships%C2%A0meant%20exploring%20varied%20fields%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20gaming%20to%20fintech.%20I%20also%20got%20to%20intern%20at%20companies%20of%20different%20scales%2C%20from%20early-stage%20startups%20to%20mature%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20summer%20internship%20I%20did%20at%20Waterloo%20was%20at%20Google.%20Interning%20there%20was%20an%20eye-opening%20experience.%20I%20got%20to%20work%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Search%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20product%20that%20billions%20of%20people%2C%20including%20myself%2C%20use%20every%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20took%20up%20the%20internship%2C%20like%20any%20freshman%2C%20I%20just%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20cool%20to%20work%20at%20a%20big%20company%20and%20ship%20big%20products.%20I%20ended%20up%20interning%20at%20Google%20twice%2C%20first%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202019%2C%20and%20then%20during%20the%20following%20summer%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20internships%20at%20Google%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%2C%20particularly%20about%20operating%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20on%20large-scale%20products.%20That%20included%20learning%20how%20to%20write%20unit%20tests%20and%20good%20technical%20design%20documents.%20Big%20companies%20are%20great%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20I%20didn't%20enjoy%20the%20bureaucracy%20that%20came%20with%20working%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-amazon-google-embrace-flatter-structure-fewer-managers-boost-efficiency-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20company.%20If%20you%20are%20shipping%20something%20on%20Google%20Search%2C%20you%20cannot%20break%20Google%20Search.%20That%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20underlying%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20understand%20why%20things%20have%20to%20be%20slow%20at%20that%20scale.%20It's%20just%20that%20for%20someone%20who%20wants%20to%20learn%20fast%20and%20try%20out%20different%20things%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20limiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20for%20my%20internship%20projects%2C%20it%20took%20a%20few%20months%20just%20for%20the%20code%20to%20get%20shipped.%20Although%20the%20projects%20were