20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20startup%20that%20was%20in%20a%20relatively%20early%20stage%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamp%20was%20at%20a%20much%20more%20mature%20stage%20than%20Warp%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20was%20focused%20on%20scaling%20up.%20Warp%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20still%20trying%20to%20figure%20things%20out.%20On%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20a%20startup%20goes%20through%20that%20process.%20I%20wanted%20to%20grapple%20with%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20does%20pricing%20work%3F%20How%20does%20the%20business%20model%20work%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20harder%20to%20see%20at%20a%20mature%20startup%2C%20where%20all%20of%20these%20things%20have%20already%20been%20figured%20out%20and%20growth%20is%20the%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20working%20at%20Warp%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20lived%20up%20to%20my%20expectations.%20We%20ship%20code%20every%20week.%20I%20could%20be%20working%20on%20something%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20it%20gets%20shipped%20out%20on%20Thursday.%20I%20work%20maybe%2060%20to%2070%20hours%20a%20week.%20It's%20a%20very%20different%20kind%20of%20velocity%20and%20cadence%20than%20at%20Big%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20near%20term%2C%20I%20want%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20on%20AI%20because%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rapidly%20expanding%20areas%20in%20tech.%20Companies%20like%20Warp%20and%20its%20competitors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwindsurf-google-cognition-acquisition-ai-coding-developer-data-ide-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECursor%20and%20Cognition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20all%20expanding%20very%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20somewhat%20tempted%20to%20launch%20my%20own%20startup%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20difficult%20to%20gain%20market%20share%20in%20this%20hyper-competitive%20space.%20That's%20something%20I%20will%20give%20serious%20thought%20about%20