3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20her%20final%20year%20of%20college%2C%20she%20encountered%20a%20rather%20major%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CAmidst%20the%20conversation%20of%20tackling%20plastic%20waste%2C%20we%20overlook%20the%20issues%20brought%20down%20by%20organic%20waste.%20About%2060%20percent%20of%20waste%20at%20home%20comprises%20organic%20waste%20that%20is%20dumped%20recklessly%20in%20landfills.%20Over%20time%2C%20this%20organic%20waste%20breaks%20down%20and%20releases%20methane%20gas%20emissions%20leading%20to%20global%20warming%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20people%20in%20urban%20spaces%20spend%20a%20lot%20on%20purchasing%20organic%20fertilisers%20as%20not%20everyone%20can%20prepare%20compost%20at%20home%20because%20of%20its%20complex%20process.%20You%20have%20to%20keep%20putting%20kitchen%20waste%20and%20soil%20in%20layers.%20It%20also%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%20as%20it%20takes%20weeks%20to%20prepare%20the%20compost%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-3-1709301271.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pavani%20has%20sold%20more%20than%206%2C000%20composting%20kits%20across%20Telangana%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Karnataka.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-3-1709301271.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-3-1709301271-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-3-1709301271-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-3-1709301271-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-3-1709301271-150