n%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1)%20Choose%20the%20right%20spot%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelect%20a%20location%20that%20gets%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20daily.%20If%20space%20is%20a%20constraint%2C%20you%20can%20also%20use%20a%20large%20pot%20or%20grow%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2)%20Prepare%20a%20nutrient-rich%20soil%20mix%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20planting%20directly%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20ensure%20the%20soil%20is%20of%20good%20quality%20and%20has%20adequate%20drainage%20to%20prevent%20waterlogging.%20You%20can%20use%20a%20potting%20mix%20in%20a%207%3A3%20ratio%20of%20soil%20to%20cow%20dung%20or%20opt%20for%20organic%2C%20nutrient-rich%20soil%20when%20planting%20in%20a%20pot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInclude%20ingredients%20like%20cow%20dung%20powder%2C%20neem%20cake%2C%20lime%2C%20and%20kitchen%20waste%20for%20an%20organic%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20seeds%20germinate%20in%20about%20a%20week.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20jackfruit%20germinate%20in%20about%20a%20week.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3)%20Selecting%20a%20sapling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGet%20a%20healthy%20sapling%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20or%20try%20growing%20one%20from%20seed.%20The%20seeds%20germinate%20in%20about%20a%20week%2C%20but%20the%20cuttings%20may%20take%20more%20than%20a%20month%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355172%2Fhow-to-grow-jackfruit-at-home-easy-tips-steps-diy-guide-grow-bag-balcony-terrace-lucknow%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanted%20from%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20may%20take%20about%20seven%20years%20for%20it%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20But%20if%20you%20bring%20a%20grafted%20plant%20from%20the%20nursery%20and%20plant%20it%2C%20you%20will%20start%20getting%20fruits%20in%20about%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhijeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20gently%20place%20the%20sapling%20in%20the%20prepared%20soil%2C%20ensuring%20roots%20are%20spread%20out.%20Water%20thoroughly%20to%20settle%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20time%20for%20planting%20is%20June%20to%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Regular%20care%20and%20monitoring%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20the%20plant%20whenever%20the%20topsoil%20is%20dry.%20Check%20soil%20moisture%20and%20set%20up%20watering%20schedules.%20You%20can%20use%20organic%20pesticides%20like%20neem%20oil%20to%20protect%20from%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5)%20Harvest%20your%20jackfruits%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%20Jackfruit%20trees%20typically%20take%20three%20to%20five%20years%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20following%20these%20tips%2C%20you%20can%20enjoy%20the%20rewarding%20experience%20of%20growing%20your%20jackfruit%20tree%2C%20reaping%20its%20delicious%20and%20nutritious%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20now%2C%20and%20let%20the%20journey%20of%20nurturing%20begin!%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756557000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D493680%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20monsoon%2C%20Immerse%20in%20season%E2%80%99s%20delights%20with%20homegrown%20jackfruit.%20From%20sunlight%20to%20sapling%20care%2C%20cultivate%20this%20superfood%20using%20tips%20from%20gardeners%20Abhijeet%20Prajapati%20and%20Mini%20Sreekumar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493680%2Fhow-to-grow-jackfruit-tree-at-home-simple-ultimate-gardening-guide%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Do%20You%20Know%20This%20Kannada%20Actress%20Who%20Has%20Rescued%204000%2B%20Animals%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%E2%80%99s%20through%20her%20work%20or%20passion%2C%20Samyukta%20Hornad%20ensures%20she%E2%80%99s%20changing%20animals%E2%80%99%20lives.%20The%20actress%E2%80%99s%20work%20spans%20roles%20in%20the%20Kannada%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20she%20is%20loved%20even%20beyond%20the%20silver%20screen.%20Samyukta%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20animals%20began%20one%20day%20when%20she%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20puppy%20stuck%20in%20a%20drain.%20She%20adopted%20him%20and%20named%20him%20Gunda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fanimal-welfare-1756203932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samyukta%20Hornad%20rescues%20animals%20and%20sees%20to%20t