%20of%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20%E2%80%98Powering%20Livelihoods%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20co-conceptualised%20by%20CEEW%20(Council%20on%20Energy%2C%20Environment%20and%20Water)%20and%20Villgro%20(a%20social%20enterprise%20incubator)%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupports%20small-scale%20farmers%20and%20rural%20entrepreneurs%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20making%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy%20(DRE)%20solutions%20accessible%20through%20low-cost%20credit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A493559%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20renewable%20energy%20as%20the%20nucleus%20around%20which%20a%20web%20of%20clean%20tech%20solutions%20emerges%20%E2%80%94%20solar-powered%20water%20pumps%20for%20irrigation%2C%20solar%20silk%20reeling%20and%20spinning%20machines%2C%20biomass-powered%20cold%20storage%20units%20for%20agriculture%2C%20and%20solar%20dryers%20for%20preserving%20produce.%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20believes%20these%20solutions%20operate%20via%20a%20three-pronged%20model%3A%20they%20enhance%20productivity%2C%20reduce%20operational%20costs%2C%20and%20create%20new%20income%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20burgeoning%20number%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20and%20micro-preneurs%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20rural%20economy%20comprising%20119%20million%20farmers%20and%206.30%20crore%20MSMEs%20%E2%80%94%20coaxed%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20to%20explore%20DRE.%20Through%20cold%20storage%20solutions%2C%20solar-powered%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20solar-powered%20pedestal%20fans%2C%20and%20solar%20charge%20controllers%2C%20the%20platform%20is%20catalysing%20the%20adoption%20of%20clean%20tech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20an%20attempt%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20rural%20landscape%2C%20which%20is%20showing%20immense%20potential%20%E2%80%94%20over%20%2450%20billion%20according%20to%20the%20CEEW%20study%E2%80%94%20is%20no%20longer%20constrained%20by%20unreliable%20electricity%20access.%20Instead%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F492080%2Frang-de-peer-to-peer-lending-model-of-loans-helps-farmers-purchase-decentralised-renewable-energy-solutions-like-solar-dryers-hydroponics-units%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDRE%20technologies%20are%20being%20viewed%20as%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20Indian%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20potential%20of%20impacting%20three%20crore%20livelihoods.%20And%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20helping%20script%20this%20success%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPowering%20rural%20futures%20with%20solar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20steadily%20being%20propelled%20towards%20a%20sustainable%20future.%C2%A0%20This%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20plummeting%20costs%20of%20solar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dramatic%2095%20percent%20drop%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20solar%20photovoltaic%20modules%20from%20over%20Rs%20200%20per%20watt%20in%202010%20to%20under%20Rs%209%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2