%E2%80%99s%20business%20associates%20help%20villagers%20adopt%20and%20run%20the%20technology%20at%20every%20step.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20is%20the%20solar%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20the%20sugarcane%20crushers%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20clear%20need%20for%20them.%20Running%20on%20diesel%20is%20incredibly%20expensive.%20Even%20if%20you%20park%20the%20climate%20part%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%2C%20the%20NOX%20emissions%20(harmful%20nitrogen%20oxides%20from%20fuel%20combustion)%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%94%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20is%20someone%20grinding%20flour%20at%20Rs%2025%20a%20unit.%20Then%20again%2C%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20stable%20three-phase%20power%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20they%20go%20to%20a%20mini%20grid%20operator%2C%20where%20the%20cost%20is%20prohibitive%2C%20around%20Rs%2025%20a%20unit.%20It%20eats%20into%20their%20margins.%20So%2C%20solar%20just%20makes%20sense.%20At%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366571%2Fkalpana-sankar-hand-in-hand-india-access-to-financial-inclusion-tamil-nadu-percy-barnevik%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowering%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20empowering%20people%20to%20make%20their%20own%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20clean%20tech%20affordable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20convince%20someone%20about%20the%20power%20of%20the%20sun%2C%20take%20them%20to%20watch%20a%20real-life%20success%20story.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20any%20capital%20expense%2C%20it%20is%20challenging%20to%20convince%20a%20rural%20customer.%20Only%20when%20they%20see%20the%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20or%20when%20you%20compare%20the%20profits%20to%20the%20operating%20expenses%20will%20they%20see%20reason%20to%20adopt%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20adds.%20Purchasing%20a%20product%20that%20costs%20upwards%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20(a%20typical%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E)%20is%20not%20something%20most%20of%20them%20can%20afford%2C%20he%20reasons%2C%20pointing%20to%20how%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20working%20with%20NBFCs%20to%20unlock%20loans%20for%20these%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20earnings%20are%20about%20three%20times%20the%20monthly%20EMI.%20If%20you%20consider%20an%20oil%20expeller%20(a%20device%20that%20extracts%20oil%20from%20seeds)%2C%20the%20person%20will%20be%20making%20around%20Rs%2060%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20with%20an%20EMI%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20higher%20than%20Rs%2025%2C000%20a%20month.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20needs%20to%20give%20the%20beneficiary%20economic%20peace%20of%20mind.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20trust%20with%20real-life%20examples%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20approach%20rests%20on%20the%20same%20moral%20reckoning.%20Acknowledging%20that%20early-stage%20scepticism%20is%20common%20among%20the%20adopters%20of%20clean%20tech%2C%20Abhishek%20reasons%20that%20most%20rural%20customers%20are%20not%20aware%20that%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F422191%2Fagrivoltaics-projects-india-nashik-parbhani-delhi-issapur-solar-energy-generation-renewable-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20technologies%20are%20capable%20of%20generating%20an%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solar%20atta%20chakkis%20are%20part%20of%20DRE%20technologies%2C%20small-scale%2C%20clean%20energy%20systems%20that%20generate%20and%20distribute%20power%20close%20to%20the%20point%20of%20consumption%2C%20rather%20than%20depending%20on%20a%20central%20grid.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-493607%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolar%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20part%20of%20DRE%20technologies%2C%20small-scale%2C%20clean%20energy%20systems%20that%20generate%20and%20distribute%20power%20close%20to%20the%20point%20of%20consumption%2C%20rather%20than%20depending%20on%20a%20central%20grid.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20every%20rural%20household%20in%20the%20country%20would%20be%20familiar%20with%20a%20solar%20panel%20for%20mobile%20charging%2C%20or%20a%20solar%20lantern%2C%20they%20might%20not%20imagine%20that%20solar%20could%20be%20used%20to%20grow%20fodder%20or%20as%20a%20cold%20storage%20solution.%20So%20the%20awareness%20gap%20is%20pretty%20big.%20Until%20they%20actually%20see%20it%20in%20action%2C%20it%20might%20prove%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20decide%20to%20buy%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20programme%20comes%20in%3B%20we%20invite%20them%20to%20witness%20successful%20models.%20These%20demo%20champions%20%E2%80%94%20early%20adopters%20of%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20then%20demonstrate%20the%20technology%20to%20others%20in%20their%20area.%20Speaking%20to%20existing%20users%20gives%20them%20perspective%20and%20builds%20their%20confidence.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaveen%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20seeking%20out%20a%20solar-powered%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20gauged%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20market%20by%20speaking%20to%20other%20micro-preneurs%20who%E2%80%99d%20taken%20the%20leap%20from%20diesel%20to%20solar.%20He%20judges%20success%20by%20certain%20fundamental%20yardsticks%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20it%20work%20well%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20efficiency%20like%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20happy%20with%20your%20decision%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20confidence%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar-powered%20device%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20steady%20whirr%20of%20the%20machine%20that%20earns%20him%20Rs%2060%2C000%2Fmonth.%20After%20accounting%20for%20the%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20which%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20Naveen%20says%20his%20net%20profit%20is%20around%20Rs%2050%2C000%20a%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20adapting%20technologies%20for%20a%20semi-urban%20or%20rural%20market%20is%20crucial%2C%20Tushar%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20urban%20setting%2C%20solar%20is%20more%20for%20cost%20savings.%20Battery%20storage%20isn%E2%80%99t%20as%20crucial.%20But%20this%20changes%20when%20you%20talk%20about%20a%20rural%20audience.%20They%20need%20battery%20storage.%20Then%20there%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20part%20about%20ensuring%20that%20the%20EMIs%20are%20paid%20on%20time%20so%20that%20their%20credit%20score%20isn%E2%80%99t%20affected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20he%20says%20financial%20literacy%20is%20key.%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20has%20a%20network%20of%20business%20associates%20%E2%80%94%20people%20trusted%20in%20the%20community%20%E2%80%94%20who%20see%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20technology%20on%20the%20ground.%20Their%20impact%20has%20fanned%20out%20across%20the%20country%20with%20over%201%2C800%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsolar%2Brefrigerator%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dsolar%2Brefrigerator%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIGCAEQRRg80gEINjI0MGowajSoAgCwAgA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstallations%20of%20the%20solar%20refrigerator%3C%2Fa%3E%20pan%20India%2C%20and%20over%2040%20solar%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Through%20its%20clean%20tech%20solutions%20and%20a%20robust%20mechanism%20of%20encouraging%20adoptions%2C%20DD%20Solar%20is%20scripting%20a%20new%20age%20India%20where%20possibility%20and%20sustainability%20live%20side%20by%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceew.in%2Fpublications%2Fhow-decentralised-renewable-energy-technologies-impact-livelihoods-in-india%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98How%20Decentralised%20Renewable%20Energy-powered%20Technologies%20Impact%20Sustainable%20Livelihoods%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20CEEW%2C%20Published%20on%209%20April%202025.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%2